snippet.title: Armored Core 2 - Intro
snippet.description:
This is the intro video that is played for Armored Core 2.

If you're a fan of the AC series, you should consider stopping by ACU!  It's a great way to get to know other fans of AC!

http://www.armoredcoreuniverse.net/
